permafrost.tundra.data

Class IDataAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wm.util.data.MemData
      • com.wm.data.ISMemDataImpl
        • permafrost.tundra.data.IDataAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.wm.data.IData, com.wm.data.IDataPortable, com.wm.util.coder.IDataCodable, com.wm.util.coder.ValuesCodable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IDataMap

    public class IDataAdapter
extends com.wm.data.ISMemDataImpl
implements com.wm.data.IData, com.wm.util.coder.IDataCodable, com.wm.data.IDataPortable, com.wm.util.coder.ValuesCodable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    A convenience wrapper for an IData object, that implements the IData, IDataCodable, IDataPortable, and ValuesCodable interfaces for maximum API compatibility.
    See Also:
